{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What is \u201cUNION SURVIVORS\u201d?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/multi.gif?t=1738296117\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;UNION SURVIVORS&quot; is a roguelite mining survival game that supports online cooperative play for up to 4 players. <br>Players dig through slime-filled terrain to carve their paths and defeat hordes of enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Possibilities for Character Development Are Endless</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/battle.gif?t=1738296117\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players defeat enemies and choose from a variety of level-up options to enhance their characters' abilities. <br>As characters level up, new weapons are unlocked, further strengthening their combat power. <br>Each weapon and level-up choice influences the build, making every challenge a unique experience and ensuring no two playthroughs are alike. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Mine Resources And Race Across The Field!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/mining.gif?t=1738296117\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slimes blocking the path may contain essential resources needed to strengthen characters or provide healing items.<br>Instead of always taking the safest route, players are encouraged to forge their own paths and face challenges head-on.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738296117","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/page.bg.jpg?t=1738296117","capsule_